-- Radian to sell financial guaranty business to Assured Guaranty
-- By Neha Dimri in Bengaluru
-- Tue Dec 23, 2014 08:53AM EST
-- None



Dec 23 (Reuters) - U.S. private mortgage insurer Radian Group Inc <RDN.N> said it would sell its financial guaranty insurance unit to Assured Guaranty Ltd <AGO.N> for $810 million.

